metadata.name: Nuke Globe
metadata.description:
2K Square (2048x2048px), 24 FPS, 10sec, Seamless Loop

A nuke captured and contained inside globe. The first NFT of mini lands and first time ever in embarking with NFTs. Explosions had always been my specialty and were always so cool to create when I first started my FX artist career.

Done with Houdini and Redshift.
